1 a child support obligation upon the applicant or license holder.;
2 (14) failed to pay any state income tax or comply with any
3 administrative or court order directing payment of state income tax.;
4 (15) except as otherwise permitted by law, rebated the whole or any
5 part of any insurance premium or offered in connection with the
6 presentation of any contract of insurance any other inducement not
