12 (17) failed to respond to an inquiry from the commissioner within 15
13 business days, or failed to respond to an inquiry within 14 calendar days
14 from the commissioner concerning a complaint, as defined in K.S.A. 40-
15 2404, and amendments thereto, or an inquiry related to a particular
